title: 'Not a pack of 2 and not even doted grid'
body: I received this product today and unfortunately, I must express my dissatisfaction. While the product itself is satisfactory, I found two significant issues. Firstly, Amazon's claim that it was a pack of two products turned out to be false, as only one item was included in the package. Additionally, the product's description mentioned it had a dotted grid, but upon inspection, I discovered that it lacked this feature. These discrepancies have left me disappointed and questioning the trustworthiness of the information provided by Amazon.
